sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    title Phase 2: Aggregating & Binding Configs
    
    participant Context as InputContextComp
    participant InputMgr as InputBindingManager
    participant P_Bridge as PlayerInputBridge
    participant PawnBridge as PawnInputBridge
    participant UE_Input as EnhancedInputSystem

    Context->>InputMgr: Trigger: Ready State Reached

    Note over InputMgr: 複数のソースからConfigを収集

    InputMgr->>P_Bridge: GetInputConfig()
    P_Bridge-->>InputMgr: Return [Menu, Move, Look]

    InputMgr->>PawnBridge: GetInputConfig()
    PawnBridge-->>InputMgr: Return [Jump, Skill_A, Vehicle_Fire]

    Note over InputMgr, UE_Input: UEのシステムへ登録開始

    InputMgr->>UE_Input: Add Mapping Context (IMC)

    loop For Each Action in Configs
        alt is Native Action (Move/Look)
            InputMgr->>UE_Input: Bind to ControlComponent Functions
        else is Ability Action (GAS)
            InputMgr->>UE_Input: Bind to RouterComponent::RouteInputTag
        end
    end